com.alexkasko.unsafe.offheaplong

Class OffHeapLongBinarySearch.IndexRange

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.alexkasko.unsafe.offheaplong.OffHeapLongBinarySearch.IndexRange
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    OffHeapLongBinarySearch

    public static class OffHeapLongBinarySearch.IndexRange
extends Object
implements Serializable
    OffHeapAddressable index range representation. Was made mutable to prevent new object instantiation for each search. isEmpty() method should be checked before accessing indices. Empty range will contain negative equal indices which values are -index - 1 where the element would be inserted. Range with size 1 will contain equal indices.
